That was so kind of you.

1443
01:52:06,205 --> 01:52:09,855
May God give you back, miss.

1444
01:52:10,377 --> 01:52:14,131
He's my whole life, mister.
Thank you so much.

1445
01:52:14,966 --> 01:52:16,322
You gave me my life back.

1446
01:52:16,635 --> 01:52:19,555
He's all I've got.

1447
01:52:20,286 --> 01:52:22,163
Come on, mom, stop it.

1448
01:52:24,666 --> 01:52:26,335
Get up, let's go.

1449
01:52:36,451 --> 01:52:38,788
Did you take all your stuff, dad?
Where's your cellphone?

1450
01:52:39,789 --> 01:52:40,832
Car keys.

1451
01:52:41,353 --> 01:52:43,647
Where's his glasses? Don't
leave without his glasses.

1452
01:52:44,274 --> 01:52:47,297
I've got it... Come here,
I'll give it to you.

1453
01:52:47,924 --> 01:52:52,721
- You go, I'll get it.
- Majid, the glasses...

1454
01:52:55,642 --> 01:52:56,789
This way.

1455
01:52:57,520 --> 01:53:01,378
What business? You just
saved his life, son.

1456
01:53:03,048 --> 01:53:05,384
No, mister, we've put you
through enough trouble already.

1457
01:53:05,655 --> 01:53:07,219
It's nothing fancy, you know.

1458
01:53:09,201 --> 01:53:10,348
Come on, this way.

1459
01:53:11,600 --> 01:53:13,581
Well, if there's anything
to do, just let me...

1460
01:53:14,103 --> 01:53:16,606
No, let him come himself.
Come on, this way.

1461
01:53:25,991 --> 01:53:27,243
You guys go.

1462
01:53:38,192 --> 01:53:40,173
Majid. Let me...

1463
01:54:26,888 --> 01:54:29,056
How much money did you leave
in the room, that night?

1464
01:54:29,287 --> 01:54:31,164
Huh?

1465
01:54:31,790 --> 01:54:33,460
How much money did you
leave in the room?

1466
01:54:34,503 --> 01:54:35,232
I didn't count.

1467
01:55:55,522 --> 01:55:56,982
What happened, dad?

1468
01:55:57,921 --> 01:56:00,007
What happened to you?
Oh, my God!

1469
01:56:01,780 --> 01:56:04,179
What happened to you?
He's sick again.

1470
01:56:04,492 --> 01:56:07,621
What are these?
Where were these?

1471
01:56:08,039 --> 01:56:10,249
- Come on, sit down a little.
- Is it your heart, dad?

1472
01:56:12,315 --> 01:56:15,964
Let him sit for a while.
Come on, this way.

1473
01:56:18,051 --> 01:56:20,553
We can't take him like this. Majid!

1474
01:56:20,762 --> 01:56:21,909
Majid, hurry up!

1475
01:56:34,214 --> 01:56:36,508
- We're almost there, dad.
- Esmat!

1476
01:56:36,822 --> 01:56:38,386
I'm hear, dear.

1477
01:56:40,681 --> 01:56:41,723
Come on, mom.

1478
01:56:42,246 --> 01:56:44,018
Watch it, don't drop him.

1479
01:56:46,939 --> 01:56:50,067
- Esmat! Esmat!
- What? Darling, I'm here.

1480
01:56:51,112 --> 01:56:53,197
What happened to you?
Ya Abalfazl!

1481
01:56:54,658 --> 01:56:55,701
Stretch his legs.

1482
01:57:02,585 --> 01:57:04,712
- God! Dad! You hear me? Dad!
- Where are his pills?

1483
01:57:06,757 --> 01:57:09,572
